  "title": "Director of Commercial",
  "description": "<p>We are a Singapore-based food &\nbeverage (F&B) company engaged in restaurant operations, brand development,\nand market expansion.</p><p>Job Title: Director of Commercial   </p><p>Employment Type: Full-time  </p><p>Location: Singapore  </p><p>Monthly Salary Range: SGD 12,000 – SGD\n15,000  </p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>- Develop and execute brand positioning and\nmarket expansion strategies  </p><p>- Identify new business opportunities,\npartnerships, and growth channels  </p><p>- Lead marketing campaigns, digital\nmarketing initiatives, and promotional activities  </p><p>- Conduct market research and consumer\ntrend analysis in the F&B sector  </p><p>- Manage brand image, customer engagement,\nand marketing performance metrics  </p><p>- Support new outlet launches and enhance\nbrand visibility  </p><p>- Work closely with operations team to\nalign marketing with business growth  </p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Degree in Marketing, Business, or related\nfield  </p><p>- At least 10 years of experience in brand\nmanagement, market development, or business growth roles  </p><p>- Experience in F&B, retail, or\nconsumer-facing industries preferred  </p><p>- Strong analytical, communication, and\nproject management skills  </p><p>- Knowledge of Singapore consumer market is\nan advantage</p>",
